  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49003814/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u49003814-2.jpg" class="pil" alt="Dreamboat" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/49003814/">Dreamboat</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          6月17日          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
      <br/>


          <span class="">有些独到的见解，也引用了不少史书佐证，只是总带着一些明显含酸捏醋的意味在书里，略感不适。</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
